%% 3.2.8 Edit Pickup Point — sequence (layered)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (Pickup Points)
    participant Goong as Goong Map API
    participant SC as Controller (BusStationController)
    participant SS as Service (BusStationService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository BusStation)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    UI->>SC: GET /api/BusStation/Get/{id}
    SC-->>UI: current station

    loop Relocate search
        Actor->>UI: Type new address
        UI->>Goong: Autocomplete
        Goong-->>UI: suggestions
    end

    Actor->>UI: Save Update
    UI->>SC: PUT /api/BusStation/Update/{id} BusStationUpdateDto

    alt BR04 duplicate within 5 m (implement in BusStationService if not yet)
        SS->>Repo: Query nearby stations
        SS-->>SC: throw
        SC-->>UI: 400
    else OK
        SS->>Repo: UPDATE
        Repo->>DB: UPDATE BusStations
        SC-->>UI: 200
    end
